Nyiseche manono kod Nyasaye ma adiera


1  Un jo-Israel winjuru wach ma Ruoth Nyasaye osewachonu: 
2  “Kik uluw timbe ogendini mamoko, kendo kik chunyu parre kuom honni muneno e kor polo, kata obedo ni gimiyo ogendini parore. 
3  Gik ma jogo lamo gin gik manono, nimar gin mana yien motong’ e bungu, kendo japecho payogi mana gi koyo, eka obawogi gi fedha kod dhahabu, 
4  kendo oriwogi gi musmal mondo kik giwuore. 
5  Gichalo gi gik mibwogogo winy e pwothe nikech ok ginyal wuoyo. Iting’ogi ating’a nimar ok ginyal wuotho, omiyo kik uluorgi nimar ok ginyal hinyou, to bende onge gima ber ma ginyalo timo.”


6  A Ruoth Nyasaye, onge ng’ato machal kodi, iduong’ kendo nyingi bende duong’. 
7  

A Ruodh ogendini duto, ere ng’ama ok diluori, nikech in iwinjori gi luor. Kuom jorieko duto mag ogendini, kata kuom ruodhigi duto, onge ng’ato maromo kodi. 
8  Giduto gifuwo kendo gionge rieko, nikech giyudo riekogi manono mana kuom yien mopa! 
9  Kido magi manonogo obaw gi fedha mogol Tarshish, kendo gi dhahabu mogol Ufaz. Gin mana tich lwedo. Irwakogi gi lewni mambulu gi maralik, ka jachuech molony ema ochueyo.


10  To Ruoth Nyasaye e Nyasaye maradier. En e Nyasaye mangima, kendo ruoth mochwere. Ka okecho to piny yiengni, kendo ogendini ok nyal siro mirimbe.


11  Nyaka inyis jogo ni nyiseche mane ok ochueyo polo gi piny ibiro kethi. Ok ginichak gibed kamoro amora e piny. 
12  Ruoth Nyasaye nochueyo piny gi tekone, mogure motegno kendo noyaro polo gi riekone. 
13  Omiyo pi man e tok polo wuo, kendo otugo boche polo e tung’ piny duto. Bende omiyo polo mil ka koth chue, kendo ogolo yamo kar kenone mondo okudhi. 
14  Gik ma kamago miyo ji ng’eng’, kendo bedo mofuwo. Jotheth duto yudo wichkuot kuom gik ma githedho, nikech gin mana nyiseche manono, ma onge gi ngima. 
15  Gin gik manono moromo chayo, kendo gibiro rumo, chieng’ ma Ruoth Nyasaye biro mondo otiekgi. 
16  Nyasach Jakobo to ok chal gi gigo, nimar en ema ochueyo gik moko duto, kendo oseyiero jo-Israel mondo obed joge owuon. Ruoth Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto e nyinge.

Masira ma biro mako jo-Juda


17  “Un jo-Jerusalem ma osetimnigi ageng’a, chokuru giu, 
18  nimar Ruoth Nyasaye owacho ni obiro golo ji duto modak e pinyni, kendo obiro sandou nyaka urum pep.” 
19  Jo-Jerusalem ywak niya, “Mano kaka wahinyore malit, kendo adhondewa ok nyal chango, to ne waparo ni en gima wanyalo dhilgo. 
20  Hembewa osekethore chuth, kendo tonde mane otuegigo osechot. Yawuotwa duto osea modhi mabor, koro onge ng’ama odong’ ma dichak gurnwa hembewa, bende onge ng’ama nyalo lieronwa rageng’ni maggi.”


21  Jeremia nodwokogi niya, “Jotelo mau onge gi rieko, nikech ok gipenj wach kuom Ruoth Nyasaye. Mano emomiyo ok gisetimo gimoro maber, kendo jowa oseke kuonde duto. 
22  Winjuru! Wach osebiro! Koko maduong’ timore e piny moro yo nyandwat. Gin jolweny mabiro ketho miech Juda, mi lokre thim ma ondiegi ema dakie. 
23  A Ruoth Nyasaye, ang’eyo ni ngima ng’ato ok nie tekone owuon, bende onge ng’ama nyalo yiero yore owuon. 
24  Kuom mano, A Ruoth Nyasaye, riewa gi bura, to ok gi mirimbi, nono to itiekowa pep. 
25  Ol mirimbi kuom ogendini ma ok oyie kuomi. Ee, kech kod jogo ma ok lami! Gisenegowa, wan nyikwa Jakobo, mi gitiekowa duto, kendo giketho pinywa.”

